data.description: Price Reduced!! Excellent opportunity for anyone starting off.  This spacious 1 bedroom 1 bath condominium is on the 2nd floor and has a lovely partial view of the San Gabriel Mountains from the balcony. One of the nicer complexes in Montebello featuring parklike walkways with mature trees and community Pool and spa and club house. Unit Features a spacious living room with dining area, both with vaulted ceilings and cozy kitchen, a spacious bedroom with new carpet and paint and plenty of closet space and a full bath with tub and shower. Single car garage below and some guest parking with parking on Neil Armstrong st. This Condo is near the new monterey park market place with Home Depot, Costco, and all the new fast food restaurants and also walking distance to Potrero Heights Park and the Shops at Montebello shopping center.
